*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT ZABAP_53_G07.

DATA: gv_carrid TYPE scarr-carrid VALUE 'AA',
      gv_fname TYPE string.

FIELD-SYMBOLS <fs> TYPE any.

PARAMETERS: pa_car TYPE scarr-CARRID.

GV_FNAME = 'GV_CARRID'.

ASSIGN GV_FNAME to <FS>.
WRITE:/ <FS>.

* GV_FNAME 변수에 <FS> field symbol이 포인터함.
ASSIGN (GV_FNAME) to <FS>.
WRITE:/ <FS>.

gv_fname = 'PA_CAR'.
ASSIGN (GV_FNAME) TO <FS>.
WRITE:/ <FS>.